## Feature workflow

[development-process.mdc](development-process.mdc): feature analysis → task break → **explicit task approval** → TDD (per approved task) → tiered runs ([issues-testing.mdc](issues-testing.mdc)) → **Feature checklist recheck** → `mvn verify` ([issues-quality.mdc](issues-quality.mdc)).

**Answering Q*n* is not approval.** After open questions are resolved, stop and wait for the user to approve task IDs before editing `src/main` or `src/test`.

## TDD — mandatory in phase 4

**Required** for every approved task. Write a failing test before `src/main` changes. The changelog **Test coverage** checklist must be complete and the **Feature checklist** rechecked before marking the entry `done` — see [development-process.mdc](development-process.mdc) § Phase 4.

Delegate to [`.cursor/agents/`](../agents/) or invoke by name (`tdd-red`, `tdd-green`, `tdd-refactor`).

| Phase | Subagent | Goal | Allowed | Forbidden |
|-------|----------|------|---------|-----------|
| **Red** | `tdd-red` | **Create** a failing test | New/updated test; domain-named methods | Production `src/main` changes |
| **Green** | `tdd-green` | Minimal code to pass | Smallest `src/main` diff | New tests; refactors; scope creep |
| **Refactor** | `tdd-refactor` | Improve design, tests green | Rename, extract, dedupe | Behaviour change |

**Cycle:** Red (must fail) → Green (must pass) → Refactor → `mvn test` → repeat.

**Session end:** every TDD cycle in progress must reach **Green** (or be reverted) before stopping — see [development-process.mdc](development-process.mdc) § Working code invariant.

Test layout: [issues-tests.mdc](issues-tests.mdc). Running tests: [issues-testing.mdc](issues-testing.mdc).
